<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 45.0pt; text-align: justify;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">направление подготовки</span></strong><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">_________________________</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 45.0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 45.0pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16.0pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>
